                <note rend="inline" type="source">819.51A/13: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Panama</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Price</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Panama</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-03-28T10:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 28, 1921—10 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 2:15 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>78. Department’s 29, March 16, 5 p.m., complied with. I was authorized Saturday
                    through Panaman Minister for Foreign Affairs to offer $12,000 salary to Fiscal
                    Agent Ruan to continue but latter refuses renewal of contract for less than
                    $15,000. I shall continue pressing matter.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Price</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
